```plantuml
@startuml annashres_CustomerBot

!define AZURE_COLOR #0072C6
!define POWERBI_COLOR #F2C811

skinparam component {
  BackgroundColor<<Azure>> AZURE_COLOR
  BorderColor<<Azure>> #0063A8
  BackgroundColor<<PowerBI>> POWERBI_COLOR
  BorderColor<<PowerBI>> #D4AB0A
}

[Bot Framework Channels] as Channels
[Azure Bot Service] <<Azure>> as BotService
[MAAV Bot] as Bot
[Adaptive Cards] as Cards
[Azure SQL Database] <<Azure>> as Database
[Power BI Dashboard] <<PowerBI>> as PowerBI

database "Auth Codes DB" as AuthDB
database "Conversation Data DB" as ConvDB

Channels --> BotService : User input
BotService --> Bot : Process messages
Bot --> Cards : Generate UI
Bot --> Database : Store/Retrieve data
Database --> AuthDB : Verify auth codes
Database --> ConvDB : Manage conversation data
Bot --> PowerBI : Provide data for visualization

note right of Bot
  Handles:
  - Conversation recording
  - Multi-channel support
  - Interactive & batch data entry
  - User authentication
  - Fuzzy company matching
  - Email parsing
  - Template generation
end note

note bottom of Database
  Stores:
  - User auth codes
  - Conversation details
  - Company information
end note

@enduml
```